{"tid":1049153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台駐日外交官自殺　日媒採訪半年　細說關西機場假新聞事件","createTime":"2019-03-06T05:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T19:15:29.000Z","uid":19527,"like":69,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"bc1b42e4be6c04ebb7d56b62174175bb7735697d","tid":1049153,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"台灣外交部駐大阪辦事處前處長蘇啟誠，去年9月13日自殺身亡，日本放送協會（NHK）周二晚在《Close up現代》節目，播放經過半年採訪、以〈假新聞害死外交官〉專題的報道，邀請專家發表看法，希望從中記取教訓。<br />\n<br />\n節目先播放蘇啟誠擔任駐日代表處那霸分處處長時，盡心盡力的外交工作，扮演台灣與日本橋樑的努力情況。節目指，蘇啟誠的自殺，與去年9月4日颱風「飛燕」吹襲大阪關西機場後，互聯網上擴散的假新聞有關。當時有3000名旅客受困機場，三分一是外籍旅客，包括中國及台灣人。當時有人在網上稱，9月5日，中國駐日大使館派出巴士到關西機場，優先將中國旅客載離機場，貼文還有附有動畫，對中國大使館的應對大力讚揚。到了翌日所有旅客脫困，有關貼文仍然繼續增加。<br />\n<br />\n節目指出，有台灣民眾當時在網上留言，認為中國大使館很努力，台灣駐日代表處卻沒做事。之後，網民大罵台灣外交官是垃圾，並讚中國的力量強大。事實上，將受困旅客撤出關西機場的巴士，都是關西機場公司安排。節目回播去年9月7日台北有立法委員舉行記者會，嚴厲追究外交部駐日代表處大阪辦事處責任的畫面，又稱台灣網民、政治人物、名嘴也追究駐日官員的責任。一名曾在網上留言的台灣男子，以匿名方式接受節目採訪，表示有7、8名朋友討論「中國派出大巴士接旅客」這條留言，以為內容是真的。<br />\n<br />\n在節目中，旅日台僑王輝生醫生接受採訪。關西機場風災後，王輝生寫電郵給蘇啟誠說，關西機場關閉，中國的巴士根本不可能進得去，中國沒有派巴士到關西機場接人。節目中，王輝生掏出手機，找出當時與蘇啟誠的對話讓記者拍攝，蘇啟誠當時回應寫道，「所言甚是，同感，但沒人聽進去」。王輝生說，他覺得蘇啟誠當時似有百口莫辯的感覺。在回覆王輝生的兩天後，蘇啟誠自殺身亡。<br />\n<br />\n節目取得蘇啟誠家人的聲明，表示：<br />\n<br />\n「希望一個外交官的犧牲，能引起台灣及日本政府有關當局、新聞媒體及相關法律的研究者對網上假新聞、假消息的流竄，在制度面上或法律面上能慎重思考如何妥當應對，防止不必要的社會混亂或者是無辜的人名譽受損。」<br />\n<br />\n為探討假消息扭曲社會的危險，節目採訪電影《FAKE》的導演森達也。他表示，毫無疑問，這宗事件的背景，與台灣與中國關係緊張有關。他說，造假在某種意義上來說，是希望符合某些人的願望。不論是媒體或網絡，都應靠自己辨識是否是真相，受眾也都要一同參與事實查核。<br />\n<br />\n台灣師範大學政研所教授范世平在社交媒體留言說，台灣早就沒人提蘇啟誠了，日本卻還關心，這突顯日本人的深入與用心，也反映台灣人的膚淺與輕慢。他表示，蘇啟誠去年9月13日輕生，日本放送協會採訪東京、大阪、沖繩及台灣等地相關人士，為了台灣一個悲劇，花了半年走訪各地，用半小時節目詳盡分析，台灣卻做不到，這是台灣傳媒的悲哀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/18862/蘇啟誠-颱風飛燕-關西機場-18862/蘇啟誠\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F18862%2F%E8%98%87%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%A0-%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E9%A3%9B%E7%87%95-%E9%97%9C%E8%A5%BF%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4-18862%2F%E8%98%87%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%A0&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=e957d1b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/18862/蘇啟誠-颱風飛燕-關西機場-18862/蘇啟誠</a>"},{"pid":"d4c3be890ee64f9d46634a7c4133bf81a6603961","tid":1049153,"uid":51271,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"台灣記者IQ只有20，日日諗住發大財"},{"pid":"6bef4974a30e1edf7c5446b86d4777328419e51e","tid":1049153,"uid":191815,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d4c3be890ee64f9d46634a7c4133bf81a6603961","tid":1049153,"uid":51271,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"台灣記者IQ只有20，日日諗住發大財"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"就算真係發大財有佢份咩 記者咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fc215360475086f456265cdf06815d32eca8ccd","tid":1049153,"uid":19527,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"6bef4974a30e1edf7c5446b86d4777328419e51e","tid":1049153,"uid":191815,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"d4c3be890ee64f9d46634a7c4133bf81a6603961","tid":1049153,"uid":51271,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"台灣記者IQ只有20，日日諗住發大財"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:37:25.000Z","msg":"就算真係發大財有佢份咩 記者咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:39:19.000Z","msg":"日日報風化新聞就真"},{"pid":"3e4f95e60950ffd2b2357766d88b1f10984711dd","tid":1049153,"uid":64576,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"係咪本身都已經有情緒問題<br />\n加埋嗰次導火線先搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ef4ff8be37339478e3d419caa2eefd398ffdcc","tid":1049153,"uid":41906,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"成個社會冇人對真相有興趣<br />\n睇新聞只係為左睇人地仆街"},{"pid":"52ce24666f153677aced1e4d483eb538bb678a05","tid":1049153,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:07:09.000Z","msg":"同反疫苗一樣假既大把人信"},{"pid":"13ff6530770a8f3787c35a11c56c94b17459bb48","tid":1049153,"uid":224561,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"繁體支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5177ff4f2ae5570a0fd48a8c80047552a5b36d69","tid":1049153,"uid":170229,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:09:25.000Z","msg":"其實唔完全怪得人<br />\n今時今日做台灣政客一定會有中國啲網軍撚化你<br />\n無咁上下真係唔應該做"},{"pid":"96125303b1888e04184d23d0a797dfe340f21861","tid":1049153,"uid":30478,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:19:49.000Z","msg":"蘇啟誠在大阪風災期間自殺身亡，死因一度成為外界討論焦點。蘇啟誠遺孀在周四出面駁斥部分政治人物故意誤導，模糊事實真相，<span style=\"color: red;\">透露丈夫並未在遺書中言及是輿論及假新聞造成壓力，反而是上級要求寫檢討報告後，「不想受到羞辱」，以死明志。蘇啟誠遺孀坦言，「希望他們以後對職業外交官有一定的尊重」。</span><br />\n<br />\n據悉，蘇啟誠自殺當天翌日，原定是由台駐日代表謝長廷開會檢討關西機場事件。不過在事發前一天，蘇啟誠接到來自外交部的電話，說明對他就關西機場事件的<span style=\"color: red;\">懲處方式，包括調回外交部、記小過，以及駐大阪辦事處全館人員的年度考績都將劃為「丙等」等，且懲處已經向總統府報告。</span><br />\n<br />\n蘇啟誠遺孀更透露，蘇啟誠自殺前曾致電訴苦，並稱有可能會被調回台灣，當時雖有安慰「沒有關係，反正快退休了」，但<span style=\"color: red;\">蘇啟誠卻表明「我無法忍受。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/273815/%E5%8F%B0%E9%A7%90%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%98%87%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%A0%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E9%9D%9E%E5%9B%A0%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E9%9C%B8%E5%87%8C-%E9%81%BA%E5%AD%80-%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F273815%2F%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%25A7%2590%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E8%2598%2587%25E5%2595%259F%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E8%2587%25AA%25E6%25AE%25BA-%25E9%259D%259E%25E5%259B%25A0%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1%25E9%259C%25B8%25E5%2587%258C-%25E9%2581%25BA%25E5%25AD%2580-%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%25A4%2596%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E9%2583%25A8%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhQexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=d0b18650\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/273815/%E5%8F%B0%E9%A7%90%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E8%98%87%E5%95%9F%E8%AA%A0%E8%87%AA%E6%AE%BA-%E9%9D%9E%E5%9B%A0%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E9%9C%B8%E5%87%8C-%E9%81%BA%E5%AD%80-%E6%98%AF%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E7%9A%84%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1</a>"},{"pid":"86445f76724285f70469b0560570b0b32d01dca9","tid":1049153,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"日本人每事每物都 dig 到好撚深入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc84578909d22f6d5c3a4ca7efb6625aea83fae9","tid":1049153,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"86445f76724285f70469b0560570b0b32d01dca9","tid":1049153,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"日本人每事每物都 dig 到好撚深入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:28:40.000Z","msg":"Tokyo hot 精神"},{"pid":"71be2eaffeb5e135fc468b3b16b9060f8ba7b630","tid":1049153,"uid":24345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"13ff6530770a8f3787c35a11c56c94b17459bb48","tid":1049153,"uid":224561,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"繁體支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T06:29:24.000Z","msg":"屌那媽明明依單fake news 係支那喺後面搞"},{"pid":"2a403dfb384d23c33aae0e12ea2551df13608585","tid":1049153,"uid":224561,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"71be2eaffeb5e135fc468b3b16b9060f8ba7b630","tid":1049153,"uid":24345,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"13ff6530770a8f3787c35a11c56c94b174